t\t<\/span>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/a>\n\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bc5e422 e-con-full e-flex e-con e-child\" data-id=\"bc5e422\" data-element_type=\"container\" data-settings=\"{&quot;content_width&quot;:&quot;full&quot;}\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-bd24a8e elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"bd24a8e\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Become a Patient<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-ca673df elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"ca673df\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>At Tenderhearts Healthcare, your health is our priority, and we&#8217;re committed to providing you with exceptional care tailored to your unique needs. Becoming a member with us is a seamless process, ensuring your health is a top priority throughout the journey.<\/p><p>To get started, share your basic details, including your name, email, and mobile number. We understand the importance of connecting, so feel free to include your social media profile to enhance our understanding of you as an individual. Your date of birth allows us to celebrate milestones and tailor our care to your specific life stage.<\/p><p>Our commitment extends to ensuring your comfort and convenience. Share your address, both at home and at work, to help us facilitate. Rest assured, your information is handled with the utmost care and confidentiality.<\/p><p>As we prioritize your holistic health, we may ask for additional details such as gender and marital status. These insights empower us to provide care that aligns with your unique circumstances.<\/p><p>Trust matters; we want you to feel secure throughout your healthcare journey. While we may request payment information for billing purposes, rest assured that sensitive details are handled with industry-standard security measures.<\/p><p>Join the Tenderhearts Healthcare family today as your journey to optimal health starts here.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-d79996d elementor-widget elementor-widget-heading\" data-id=\"d79996d\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"heading.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t<h2 class=\"elementor-heading-title elementor-size-default\">Other Policies<\/h2>\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-element elementor-element-2ce8727 elementor-widget elementor-widget-text-editor\" data-id=\"2ce8727\" data-element_type=\"widget\" data-widget_type=\"text-editor.default\">\n\t\t\t\t<div class=\"elementor-widget-container\">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<p>Empower Your Financial Wellness with Tenderhearts Healthcare:<\/p><p><strong>Financial Clarity:<\/strong> Understand your financial responsibility for medical services with our Financial Policy. Your care is our priority, regardless of insurance eligibility or coverage determinations.<\/p><p><strong>Privacy Matters:<\/strong> Your privacy is crucial. Review our Notice of Privacy Practices to learn how your health information may be used and disclosed. At Tenderhearts Healthcare, your individually identifiable health information is handled with the utmost care.<\/p><p>Embark on a journey of financial clarity and privacy assurance with Tenderhearts Healthcare. We&#8217;re committed to keeping you informed and empowered in your healthcare choices.<\/p>\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<\/div>\n\t\t","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>PATIENT INFORMATION Your Journey, Our Priority. At Tenderhearts Healthc